#. Default: "Thank you for using OiRA. Before we go to the report we would
#. kindly like to ask you to give us some feedback via the survey below. This
#. information is meant to improve the tools and the services provided.
#. <strong>This data will not appear in your reports.</strong>"
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/report_company.pt:40
msgid "company_report_intro"
msgstr ""
"Hvala, ker uporabljate orodje OiRA. Preden preidemo na poročilo, vas "
"prosimo, da nam v spodnji anketi posredujete povratne informacije. Namen teh"
" informacij je izboljšati orodja in storitve. <strong>Ti podatki ne bodo "
"prikazani v vaših poročilih.</strong>"

#. Default: "For any further information regarding the handling of their
#. personal data, data subjects can address their request to EU-OSHA Data
#. Protection Officer at: dpo(at)osha.europa.eu."
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/conditions-bare.pt:110
msgid "conditions_part10_entry"
msgstr ""
"Če želijo posamezniki, na katere se nanašajo osebni podatki, prejeti dodatne"
" informacije glede obdelave svojih osebnih podatkov, lahko svojo zahtevo "
"naslovijo na pooblaščeno osebo za varstvo podatkov pri agenciji EU-OSHA na "
"elektronski naslov: dpo(afna)osha.europa.eu."

#. Default: "Request for information"
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/conditions-bare.pt:108
msgid "conditions_part10_header"
msgstr "Zahteva za informacije"

#. Default: "Data subjects are entitled to make recourse to the European Data
#. Protection Supervisor: ${url} , should they consider that the processing
#. operations do not comply with the Regulation."
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/conditions-bare.pt:118
msgid "conditions_part11_entry"
msgstr ""
"Posamezniki, na katere se nanašajo osebni podatki, imajo pravico, da se "
"obrnejo na evropskega nadzornika za varstvo podatkov: ${url}, če menijo, da "
"postopki obdelave niso v skladu z Uredbo (EU) 2018/1725."

#. Default: "Recourse to the EDPS"
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/conditions-bare.pt:114
msgid "conditions_part11_header"
msgstr "Stik z evropskim nadzornikom za varstvo podatkov (ENVP)"

