msgstr ""
"Prosimo, označite vse, kar bi morda želeli izključiti iz usposabljanja. "
"Elementi, ki so zatemnjeni, ne bodo prikazani na vadbeni kartici."

#. Default: "The risk evaluation has been automatically done by the tool. You
#. will be able to change the priority for this risk &ndash; if you consider
#. it necessary &ndash; in the action plan."
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/webhelpers.pt:596
