#. special characters. The new logo will only become visible after you have
#. saved your changes and published the OiRA tool."
#: euphorie/content/sector.py:72
msgid "help_logo_upload"
msgstr ""
"Logotip se bo pojavil na pregledni strani sektorja vaše države. Poskrbite, "
"da bo vaša slika v formatu png, jpg ali gif in ne vsebuje nobenih posebnih "
"znakov. Nov logotip bo viden šele, ko boste shranili spremembe in objavili "
"orodje OiRA."

#. Default: "Describe your general approach to eliminate or (if the risk is
#. not avoidable) reduce the risk. + Describe the specific action(s) required
#. to implement this approach (to eliminate or to reduce the risk)."
#: euphorie/content/solution.py:73
msgid "help_measure_action"
msgstr ""
"Opisujte svoj splošni pristop za odpravo ali (če tveganja ni mogoče "
"izogniti) zmanjšanje tveganja. + Opisujte specifične aktivnosti, potrebne za"
" izvajanje tega pristopa (za odpravo ali zmanjšanje tveganja)."

#. Default: "Describe your general approach to eliminate or (if the risk is
#. not avoidable) reduce the risk."
#: euphorie/content/solution.py:43
msgid "help_measure_action_plan"
msgstr ""
"Opišite svoj splošni pristop za preprečevanje ali (če se tveganju ni mogoče "
"izogniti) zmanjšanje tveganja."

#. Default: "Describe the specific action(s) required to implement this
#. approach (to eliminate or to reduce the risk)."
#: euphorie/content/solution.py:56
msgid "help_measure_prevention_plan"
msgstr ""
"Opišite specifična dejanja, potrebna za izvajanje tega pristopa (da "
"preprečite ali zmanjšate tveganje)."

#. Default: "Describe the level of expertise needed to implement the measure,
#. for instance \"common sense (no OSH knowledge required)\", \"no specific
#. OSH expertise, but minimum OSH knowledge or training and/or consultation of
#. OSH guidance required\", or \"OSH expert\". You can also describe here any
#. other additional requirement (if any)."
#: euphorie/content/solution.py:91
msgid "help_measure_requirements"
msgstr ""
"Opišite raven strokovnosti, potrebna za izvajanje ukrepa, npr. \"zdrava "
"pamet (znanje OSH ni potrebno)\", \"specifično strokovno znanje OSH ni "
"potrebno, vendar je potrebno minimalno poznavanje OSH ali usposabljanje "
"in/ali posvetovanje o smernicah OSH\" ali \"strokovnjak za OSH\". Tukaj "
"lahko opišete tudi morebitne druge dodatne zahteve (če obstajajo)."

#. Default: "Include any relevant information that may be helpful for the end-
#. user."
#: euphorie/content/module.py:52 euphorie/content/page.py:17
#: euphorie/content/solution.py:29
msgid "help_module_description"
msgstr ""
"Vključite vse bistvene informacije, ki bi lahko koristile končnemu "
"uporabniku."

#. Default: "Allows the end-user to skip this module and everything inside
#. it."
#: euphorie/content/module.py:64
msgid "help_module_optional"
msgstr "Končnemu uporabniku omogoča preskočiti ta modul in vse v njem."

#. Default: "The question to ask the end-user if this module is optional. It
#. must be formulated so that it is answerable with YES (the end-user will
#. have to tick a box) or NO"
#: euphorie/content/module.py:76
msgid "help_module_question"
msgstr ""
"Vprašanje, ki se postavi končnemu uporabniku, če je ta modul poljuben. "
"Oblikovati ga je treba tako, da je nanj mogoče odgovoriti z DA (končni "
"uporabnik bo moral odkljukati polje) ali NE"

#. Default: "Please enter the number of questions to be shown at the end of
#. your training session. If the number is lower than the number of existing
#. questions, the questions will be picked randomly. Empty the field to show
#. all questions."
#: euphorie/content/survey.py:237
msgid "help_num_training_questions"
msgstr ""
"Vnesite število vprašanj, ki naj se prikažejo na koncu vaše usposabljanje. "
"Če je število manjše od števila obstoječih vprašanj, bodo vprašanja izbrana "
"naključno. Izpraznite polje, da se prikažejo vsa vprašanja."

#. Default: "The password needs to be at least 12 characters long and needs to
#. contain at least one lower case letter, one upper case letter and one
#. digit."
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/login.pt:216
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/register_session.pt:203
msgid "help_password_requirements"
msgstr ""
"Geslo mora biti dolgo vsaj 12 znakov in mora vsebovati vsaj eno malo črko, "
"eno veliko črko in eno številko."

#. Default: "This text should explain the 2 types of profile questions."
#: euphorie/content/help.py:53
msgid "help_preparation"
msgstr "To besedilo mora pojasniti 2 vrsti profilnih vprašanj."

#. Default: "The preview will be available at ${url}."
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/preview.pt:29
msgid "help_preview_url"
msgstr "Predogled bo na voljo na ${url}."

#. Default: "This is the inverse of the affirmative statement (e.g. The
#. building is not well maintained.)"
#: euphorie/content/risk.py:81
msgid "help_problem_description"
msgstr ""
"To je nasprotje pritrditvene izjave (npr. Ta zgradba ni dobro vzdrževana.)"

#. Default: "Publish the selected OiRA Tool live with its latest changes."
#: euphorie/deployment/tiles/templates/versions.pt:34
msgid "help_publish"
msgstr ""
"V živo objavi izbrano orodje OiRA z njegovimi najnovejšimi spremembami."

#. Default: "After publication the OiRA Tool will be available at ${url}."
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/publish.pt:45
msgid "help_publish_url"
msgstr "Po objavi bo orodje OiRA na voljo na ${url}."

#. Default: "This text should describe how the report can either be saved or
#. printed."
#: euphorie/content/help.py:93
msgid "help_reports"
msgstr "To besedilo mora opisati, kako poročilo shraniti ali natisniti."

#. Default: "Describe the risk. Include any relevant information that may be
#. helpful for the end-user."
#: euphorie/content/risk.py:93
msgid "help_risk_description"
msgstr ""
"Opišite tveganje. Vključite vse bistvene informacije, ki bi lahko koristile "
"končnemu uporabniku."

#. Default: "\"Priority risk\" is one of the high risks in the sector.
#. \"Risk\" is related to the workplace or to the work carried out. \"Policy\"
#. refers to agreements, procedures, and management decisions."
#: euphorie/content/risk.py:148
msgid "help_risk_type"
msgstr ""
"Prioritetno tveganje\" je eno od visokih tveganj v sektorju. \"Tveganje\" je"
" povezano z delovnim mestom ali opravljanim delom. \"Politika\" se nanaša na"
" sporazume, postopke in odločitve vodstva."

#. Default: "If you do not specify a title it will be taken from the input
#. file."
#: euphorie/content/browser/upload.py:141
msgid "help_sector_title"
msgstr "Če ne specificirate naslova, bo uporabljen iz vnosne datoteke."

#. Default: "This text should describe the main functions of the OiRA Tool."
#: euphorie/content/help.py:43
msgid "help_sessions"
msgstr "To besedilo mora opisati glavne funkcije orodja OiRA."

#. Default: "Offer a `not applicable' option in addition to the standard
#. yes/no options."
#: euphorie/content/risk.py:138
msgid "help_show_notapplicable"
msgstr "Poleg standardnih možnosti da/ne ponudi možnost `ni smiselno'."

#. Default: "This information will appear in the Action plan step and should
#. include an overview of general solution(s) related to this module."
#: euphorie/content/module.py:101
msgid "help_solution_direction"
msgstr ""
"Te informacije bodo prikazane v koraku Načrt ukrepov in morajo vsebovati "
"pregled splošnih rešitev, povezanih s tem modulom."

#. Default: "Start based on an existing risk assessment. All content of the
#. existing risk assessment will be copied over into the new risk assessment,
#. which you can edit and augment at will."
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/new-session.pt:58
msgid "help_start_base_on_existing"
msgstr ""
"Začnite na podlagi obstoječe ocene tveganja. Celotna vsebina obstoječe ocene"
" tveganja se bo kopirala v novo oceno tveganja, ki jo lahko poljubno urejate"
" in dopolnjujete."

#. Default: "Start from scratch with an empty risk assessment."
#: euphorie/client/browser/templates/new-session.pt:52
msgid "help_start_from_scratch"
msgstr "Začnite od začetka s prazno oceno tveganja."

#. Default: "This is a short affirmative statement about a possible risk (e.g.
#. The building is well maintained.)"
#: euphorie/content/risk.py:69
msgid "help_statement"
msgstr ""
"To je kratka pritrditvena izjava o možnem tveganju (npr. Zgradba je dobro "
"vzdrževana.)"

#. Default: "This method involves risk assessment by Severity x Exposure,
#. whereas these have to be understood as follows; Severity of injury linked
#. to hazard - Exposure (Frequency) to the hazard"
#: euphorie/content/surveygroup.py:95
msgid "help_survey_evaluation_algorithm_simplified"
msgstr ""
"Ta metoda vključuje oceno tveganja glede na resnost x izpostavljenost, ki pa"
" mora biti razumljena takole; Resnost poškodbe, povezane z nevarnostjo - "
"Izpostavljenost (pogostost) nevarnosti"

#. Default: "This method involves risk assessment by Severity x Exposure x
#. Probability, whereas these have to be understood as follows; Severity of
#. injury linked to hazard - Exposure (Frequency) to the hazard - Probability
#. of the hazard occuring when exposed"
#: euphorie/content/surveygroup.py:76
msgid "help_survey_evaluation_algorithm_standard"
msgstr ""
"Ta metoda vključuje oceno tveganja glede na resnost x izpostavljenost x "
"verjetnost, ki pa mora biti razumljena takole; Resnost poškodbe, povezane z "
"nevarnostjo - Izpostavljenost (pogostost) do nevarnosti - Verjetnost "
"nevarnosti, ko je izpostavljena"

#. Default: "This OiRA Tool is obsolete; it has been retired or replaced with
#. another OiRA Tool."
#: euphorie/content/surveygroup.py:55
msgid "help_survey_obsolete"
msgstr ""
"Ta anketa je zastarela; bila je umaknjena, ali zamenjana z drugo anketo."

#. Default: "This is the title of this OiRA Tool version. This name is never
#. shown to users."
#: euphorie/content/survey.py:80
